 Nancy Isime Popular Nigerian media personality and actress, Nancy Isime has shared her childhood experiences and how she struggled growing up after her mum died. Nancy Isime revealed in an exclusive interview with BBC Pidgin that life was extremely difficult for her after losing her mother and she even tried committing suicide after battling depressing for a long time predominantly due to the unbearable conditions of living. The Edo-state born vlogger and brand influencer said that she began working at the age of 17 where she worked as an usher and unlike others who have time to go through life, she had no option but to be matured.